name: "In the Coils" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Felt pen, brush pen, paint pen, and liner pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and colors.] Coils and spirals. Endless digression. The macro mimics the micro. Snakes and snails and puppy-dog tails... And ink, of course... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
